*** 2.02 Release July 27, 2003

- Minor cleanups in the code, w/ a couple of GUI-fixen.

*** 2.00 Released May 27, 2002

- Search functionality added. Uses UNIX shell syntax, and searches
  through both title and ingredients for the desired term.

- Minor Bugfixes and GUI cleanups.

*** 1.1 Released April 11, 2002

- Mousewheel support added. Should work in both Unix/Linux and Windows.

- <Esc> will dismiss a View Recipe window.

- POD added to Recipe.pm

- Makefile.PL added to distribution. Should be easier to install now.

- Various GUI cleanups

- Minor bugfixes


*** 1.0	Initial Release	April 4, 2002
